<ul>
<li>[ ] Organization schema on every page (via site-wide template)</li>
<li>[ ] LocalBusiness schema on location pages (if applicable)</li>
<li>[ ] Article or BlogPosting schema on every blog post</li>
<li>[ ] BreadcrumbList schema across the entire site</li>
<li>[ ] Product schema on product and pricing pages</li>
<li>[ ] FAQPage schema on FAQ sections</li>
